data.description: Sought after Saddle Ridge location!  4 bedrooms (primary downstairs), 2 and 1 half baths, lush landscaping. Covered front and back porches, open sight lines from kitchen, dining, and living rooms.  Beautiful wood floors, designer colors, and ceiling fans, modern lighting.  Open kitchen with gas stove and cooktop, double sink, tile, LOTS of cabinets and pantry.  Large open dining area.  Primary suite with ensuite bathroom, double sinks soaking tub and separate shower.  Large walk-in closet. Game room upstairs with lots of room to entertain. Secondary bath with tub/shower combo. Half bath downstairs. Covered porch in back looking out on fenced yard.  2-car attached garage. Storage shed in backyard stays with home.
